353
00:27:10,740 --> 00:27:13,960
[SPEAKER_01] Bez dubine, bez specifične tvoje perspektive.

354
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:17,819
[SPEAKER_01] I to je ono što on... Do čega nas on može dovesti.

355
00:27:17,819 --> 00:27:22,240
