413
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:31,839
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, dobro se to sađela, apsolutno.

414
00:30:31,839 --> 00:30:34,319
[SPEAKER_01] I treba biti hrabar, u tome i treba neovisiti.

415
00:30:34,319 --> 00:30:38,660
[SPEAKER_01] A to ti je puno lakše ako neovisiš o izvoru prihoda iz establishmenta.

416
00:30:38,660 --> 00:30:41,180
